## 1. Structure
* `<!DOCTYPE html>`: Defines HTML5.
* `<html>`: Root container.
* `<head>`: Page metadata.
* `<title>`: Browser tab text.
* `<body>`: Visible content.

```html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head><title>Title</title></head>
<body><!-- Content here --></body>
</html>
```

## 2. Text
* `<h1>` to `<h6>`: Headings (Largest to smallest).
* `<p>`: Text paragraph.
* `<br>`: Line break.
* `<strong>`: Bold text.
* `<em>`: Italic text.

```html
<h1>Header</h1>
<p>Text with <strong>bold</strong> and <em>italics</em>.</p>
```

## 3. Links & Media
* `<a>`: Hyperlink. Uses `href="URL"`.
* `<img>`: Image. Uses `src="image.jpg"` and `alt="description"`.

```html
<a href="https://github.com">Link</a>
<img src="pic.jpg" alt="Logo">
```

## 4. Lists
* `<ul>`: Bulleted list.
* `<ol>`: Numbered list.
* `<li>`: List item.

```html
<ul>
  <li>Item A</li>
</ul>
<ol>
  <li>Item 1</li>
</ol>
```

## 5. Containers
* `<div>`: Block container (starts new line).
* `<span>`: Inline container (stays on same line).

